Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:45.92,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}当两人相遇之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:50.97,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}梦想还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:54.89,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知要过多长时间
